title: NFL ATL: Draft news, who's lying?
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Draft news, who's lying?
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- runs through the latest NFL Draft headlines.  Who’s trading up?  Who’s trading down?  Who’s lying?  There’s only one place to find out -- and that’s this latest installment of the "Around the League Podcast."
